{"type": "article", "id": 52341, "title": "模仿日晷的时钟，小棍是分针，影子是时针｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-04-19T23:15:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 21855, "name": "Harkavy Furniture"}, {"id": 49491, "name": "Sawaya & Moroni"}, {"id": 3970, "name": "MAD建筑事务所"}, {"id": 44603, "name": "Raw Edges"}, {"id": 242, "name": "YOY"}, {"id": 39342, "name": "Jiyoun Kim"}, {"id": 49492, "name": "Chen Chen"}, {"id": 49493, "name": "Kai Williams"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 15, "praise_count": 220, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180419183213L8sfVCoWygAh7Qla.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Sundial by YOY</h3><p>日本创意工作室 YOY 具有独特的设计风格，他们有许多依附新技术或者新材料的设计作品，给人的印象焕然一新。他们作品还具有典型的日式特点。</p><p>这是一个模仿日晷设计而成的时钟。日晷中的小棍是分针，它的影子是时针。影子是印在钟面上的，整体造型给人感觉小棍和它的影子绕着钟面在互相追逐着。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419183408uC0wcnlGRvbT3mUe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419183408TUP5qrXa1iQMRZlG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419183409dVJiPjM82DBmNXFa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://yoy-idea.jp/works/sundial/\" rel=\"nofollow\">YOY</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Stacking Planter by Chen Chen and Kai Williams</h3><p>纽约设计师 Chen Chen 和 Kai Williams 创造了一对瓷器花盆。这组堆叠式花盆包含一系列可堆叠配件，由陶瓷制成，外部没有上釉，内部装饰有玻璃。由于其是高温烧制，玻璃内饰面也是光滑的，不容易藏污纳垢。顶部堆叠单元有四个排水孔，让水从根部滴下并渗入下方。产品提供高矮两种尺寸，分别是 20 厘米和 10 厘米高。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419185032y0kNQ74RMIqz8mxd.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562992\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419183754bpNJ91lVvHW3iBmM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419183754YQvu7IyfdTNFmKRO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419183755zDaFo6vipnIZRUw8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419183756PfT4KFvJIr5aAeVt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419183756Z260D9t1FC8xgykd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/04/18/stacking-planter-conceals-water-saucer-chen-chen-kai-williams/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Horah by Raw Edges</h3><p>以一种以色列的传统舞蹈巴尔干为灵感，伦敦设计工作室 Raw Edges 设计了 30 个旋转玻璃灯，尺寸、色彩各异，构成了一个名为 Horah 的装置，亮相米兰设计周。</p><p>特别的是，30 个灯会一直慢慢旋转，所以这是一个动态装置。“我们喜欢很多东西以相同的速度一起转动的想法，比如跳舞或游泳，或者在街上行进的军队。”设计师说。</p><p>灯具的每一个玻璃片看上去都像是一片叶子，连接到一个旋转电机上。光源隐藏在中央，会在玻璃叶片上产生渐变照明的效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=w0633ewmlis&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804191849374BHcZ8lVNp3JS0wm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419184939id53JmSgMKtR2Hfw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804191849391LuehdY0Drk4zgAT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419184943cMViO4satnljgZJG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.659898\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804191849477LRtfaFG2vpHxj18.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804191849493omGVrAyYndCOQWz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>骨椅 by MAD for Sawaya &amp; Moroni</h3><p>继去年的 “蘑菇椅”后，建筑师马岩松领衔的 MAD 今年继续和意大利家具设计品牌 Sawaya &amp; Moroni合作，推出了扶手椅“骨椅”。</p><p>“骨椅”参考了人体骨骼，仿佛透射出了最自然的人体曲线。除了像是正在呼吸生长的有机体，作品同时也是一件生动的雕塑艺术品：有机的形态，完美的线条，配以经过重重打磨的木质，落落大方、优雅简约。设计显露的神秘的未来感，与有机形态毫不突兀。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804191851217JPnjepsO3di16fH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.645714\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419185121LG7dSUFo5pnJrNx8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.645714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419185121uORV0qbzN2C3Sh51.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.377143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804191851213EeB516Rp0bZy7tx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804191851200JqXLlRwemPb7ZFz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.645714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Walnut &amp; Steel Office Furniture by Harkavy Furniture</h3><p>Harkavy Furniture 是一对兄弟几年前在波特兰创立的家具品牌，其特色是通过使用实木和钢材创作出线条简洁利落的家具。其最新作品是办公家具系列，包括办公桌、书架、桌子和书柜，均由坚实的胡桃木材质和粉末涂层钢组合手工制作而成的，带来干净简约的感觉。</p><p>由于每件作品都是用手工制作的，因此它们还可以选择定制粉末涂料的色彩以及木材类型等等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419185210GKo6UYdMgZekj8yE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419185210QSIyJEUK942s3DFn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500781\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804191852103cHAoUPSxmClnRrz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419185210GI5FUM70vcWOXxkn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419185210xsfHc3J6tU0joKpm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.harkavyfurniture.com/office\" rel=\"nofollow\">Harkavy Furniture</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Lightning Lamp by Jiyoun Kim</h3><p>“晴天也会遇雷击”，韩国设计师 Jiyoun Kim 以这句韩国俗语为灵感，创作了一盏名为 Lightning 的台灯。这句话的意思是人们经常要面对意想不到的灾难，想要传达给人们的是要改变自己的看法，来克服生命进程中无处不在的挑战。</p><p>Lightning 由不锈钢经过精密的加工制作而成，捕捉了雷电击中地面一瞬间的光。灯饰的颈部是由玻璃制作而成的云层结构，采用了传统的吹制技术。它共有 4 种配色，表现了一天中四种不同时间下天空的模样，它们分别是白天、清晨、午夜以及落日时分。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804191853138OzLavP6QoMdNAIG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804191853140yEsdLMQtNxB79iS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804191853144gvNJVq23FXDjGM7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.741250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419185315h70nkwNRoXebx3UV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.787500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419185316vMirBWZ3C9m2hD41.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180419185319GbI38tE4zV5cHfCi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709375\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.jiyounkim.com/02_about.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jiyoun Kim</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}